:47:00+00:00" itemprop="commentTime"><a href="http://journalxtra.com/wordpress/top-10-ultimate-wordpress-security-plugins/comment-page-1/#comment-3806" class="comment-time-link" itemprop="url">February 13, 2012 at 3:47 PM</a></time> </p> </header> <div class="comment-content" itemprop="commentText"> <p>Yep BPS Pro works perfectly on Mobile sites.  ;)</p> </div> </article> </li> <li class="comment odd alt depth-2" id="comment-3807"> <article itemprop="comment" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/UserComments"> <header class="comment-header"> <p class="comment-author" itemprop="creator" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"> <img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/7854194ca7efa54ff1394fd69858e45d?s=96&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F1.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D96&amp;r=R' class='avatar avatar-96 photo' height='96' width='96'/><span itemprop="name"><a href="http://journalxtra.com/" class="comment-author-link" rel="external nofollow" itemprop="url">Lee Hodson</a></span> <span class="says">says</span> </p> <p class="comment-meta"> <time class="comment-time" datetime="2012-02-13T17:11:00+00:00" itemprop="commentTime"><a href="http://journalxtra.com/wordpress/top-10-ultimate-wordpress-security-plugins/comment-page-1/#comment-3807" class="comment-time-link" itemprop="url">February 13, 2012 at 5:11 PM</a></time> </p> </header> <div class="comment-content" itemprop="commentText"> <p>Good. I bought the Pro version yesterday. Will trial it and write a review. Like what I see so far. What I think is missing is an option to change the wp-content directory&#8217;s name. I&#8217;ve cut out a lot of automated hack attempts just by making that one simple change. I will amend this post to &#8220;top 11&#8243; when I get a bit of quiet time over the next few days.</p> <p>One more thing, it took me 20 minutes to find the &#8220;Pay Here&#8221; link. I was going nutty looking for it ;)</p> </div> </article> </li> <li class="